# 🎬 AI Social Media Content Studio

Autonomous social media content generation and publishing — powered by **QuickFrame AI**, **Claude**, **Stability AI**, and **Replicate**.

## ✨ Features

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| 🎨 QuickFrame AI Studio | Professional AI video creation with auto-generated briefs |
| 🤖 Claude AI | Captions, hashtags, hooks, scripts, and full content strategy |
| 🖼️ Stability AI | High-resolution image generation (SDXL) |
| 🎬 Replicate | Video generation (minimax, luma-dream-machine) |
| 📱 Multi-Platform | Instagram · TikTok · X/Twitter · LinkedIn · Facebook · YouTube Shorts |
| 🔥 Live Trends | Real-time trending topic discovery |
| 📅 Scheduling | Queue posts with repeat cadence |
| 📈 Strategy | Full 7-day content strategy generation |

---

## 🚀 Quick Deploy to Streamlit Cloud

1. **Fork this repo** → `github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/ai-social-studio`

2. **Go to** [share.streamlit.io](https://share.streamlit.io) → **New app**

3. Set:
   - **Repository**: `YOUR_USERNAME/ai-social-studio`
   - **Branch**: `main`
   - **Main file**: `app.py`

4. **Add secrets** (Settings → Secrets):

```toml
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY     = "sk-ant-..."
STABILITY_API_KEY     = "sk-..."
REPLICATE_API_KEY     = "r8_..."

# Optional — social platforms
TWITTER_API_KEY             = ""
TWITTER_API_SECRET          = ""
TWITTER_ACCESS_TOKEN        = ""
TWITTER_ACCESS_TOKEN_SECRET = ""

LINKEDIN_ACCESS_TOKEN = ""
LINKEDIN_PERSON_URN   = "urn:li:person:XXXX"

FACEBOOK_ACCESS_TOKEN = ""
FACEBOOK_PAGE_ID      = ""

INSTAGRAM_ACCESS_TOKEN = ""
INSTAGRAM_USER_ID      = ""
```

5. Click **Deploy** ✅

---

## 🔧 Local Development

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/ai-social-studio
cd ai-social-studio

python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # Windows: venv\Scripts\activate

pip install -r requirements.txt

# Create .env file
cp .env.example .env
# Add your keys to .env

streamlit run app.py
```

