## 🔑 API Keys — Where to Get Them

| Service | URL | Free Tier |
|---|---|---|
| QuickFrame AI | [ai.quickframe.com](https://ai.quickframe.com) | ✅ Free trial |
| Anthropic Claude | [console.anthropic.com](https://console.anthropic.com) | $5 free credit |
| Stability AI | [platform.stability.ai](https://platform.stability.ai) | 25 free images |
| Replicate | [replicate.com](https://replicate.com) | Pay per run ~$0.01 |
| Twitter/X | [developer.twitter.com](https://developer.twitter.com) | Free Basic tier |
| LinkedIn | [linkedin.com/developers](https://linkedin.com/developers) | Free OAuth |
| Facebook/Instagram | [developers.facebook.com](https://developers.facebook.com) | Free Graph API |

