├── utils/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── ai_generator.py       # Claude + Stability AI + Replicate
│   ├── prompt_builder.py     # Platform-optimized prompt engineering
│   ├── social_poster.py      # Social media API integrations
│   └── trending.py           # Live trending topics + presets
└── README.md
```

---

## 🔄 Workflow

```
Choose Topic (trending / preset / custom)
        ↓
Generate with Claude (caption · hashtags · hook · script)
        ↓
Generate Visual (Stability AI image / Replicate video)
        ↓
Build QuickFrame Brief (auto-filled for studio use)
        ↓
Open QuickFrame AI → generate professional video
        ↓
Publish to all platforms simultaneously
        ↓
Schedule future posts with repeat cadence
```

---

## ⚠️ Notes

- **QuickFrame AI** does not currently expose a public REST API. This app embeds it as a studio panel and auto-generates a creative brief so you can produce your video in QuickFrame in under 2 minutes. Programmatic video generation uses Replicate as a fallback.
- **Instagram** posting via Graph API requires a public image URL (CDN-hosted). For local development, upload your image to a public host first.
- **TikTok** programmatic posting requires a verified TikTok for Developers account. The app provides the content and caption for manual upload.

